projects.title: Lightening Dancer
projects.subject: Science
projects.description: Materials: 1 Pie Tin, 1 Balloon, 1 Piece of Tissue Paper, Scissors, Seran Wrap. Steps: cut out a person from the tissue paper, place in covered pie tin in seran wrap, blown up balloon, rubbed on carpet or hair, place on pie tin to make a tissue person, dance with static electricity
